metadata.name: TIKI # 1
metadata.description:
Tiki is a ancient artwork, inspired by Oceanian art, Caribbean art, and art of the east Pacific. In Polynesian mythology, tiki often represents the first human being on Earth. Tiki's are stranger , anonymous and Powerful.

Properties

Face      - Dragon
Background-  Triangle Smash 
Neck      -  Ancient
Tattoo    -  House
